  "strings": [
    {
      "widget_id": "d9foc4n3",
      "type": "html",
      "field": "html",
      "fr": "<div class=\"kv-eyebrow\"><span class=\"kv-eyebrow-bar\"></span>INDUSTRIE · MANUFACTURIER</div>",
      "en": "<div class=\"kv-eyebrow\"><span class=\"kv-eyebrow-bar\"></span>INDUSTRY · MANUFACTURING</div>"
    },
    {
      "widget_id": "6356eisy",
      "type": "heading",
      "field": "title",
      "fr": "Optimiser votre <em style=\"font-family:Fraunces,serif;font-style:italic;color:#C9A35C;font-weight:600\">efficacité</em> manufacturière.",
      "en": "Optimize your manufacturing <em style=\"font-family:Fraunces,serif;font-style:italic;color:#C9A35C;font-weight:600\">efficiency</em>."
    },
    {
      "widget_id": "2jpycnr7",
      "type": "text-editor",
      "field": "editor",
      "fr": "<p>Au cœur d'un site de production performant se trouvent une planification rigoureuse, une traçabilité fiable et une collaboration fluide entre l'ingénierie et l'atelier. Nous vous aidons à mettre en place les outils pour y parvenir.</p>",
      "en": "<p>At the heart of a high-performing production site lie rigorous planning, reliable traceability, and seamless collaboration between engineering and the workshop. We help you put the right tools in place to achieve this.</p>"
    },
    {
      "widget_id": "n5duwltm",
      "type": "html",
      "field": "html",
      "fr": "<span class=\"kv-badge\">◆ Solutions PDM, CAO & Collaboration</span>",
      "en": "<span class=\"kv-badge\">◆ PDM, CAD & Collaboration Solutions</span>"
    },
    {
      "widget_id": "nbpklmgr",
      "type": "button",
      "field": "text",
      "fr": "Voir nos solutions",
      "en": "View our solutions"
    },
    {
      "widget_id": "igmpb0og",
      "type": "button",
      "field": "text",
      "fr": "Nous contacter",
      "en": "Contact us"
    },
    {
      "widget_id": "3zl7g9xp",
      "type": "heading",
      "field": "title",
      "fr": "Vos défis <em style=\"font-family:Fraunces,serif;font-style:italic;color:#C9A35C;font-weight:600\">quotidiens</em>",
      "en": "Your daily <em style=\"font-family:Fraunces,serif;font-style:italic;color:#C9A35C;font-weight:600\">challenges</em>"
    },
    {
      "widget_id": "h89yu87y",
      "type": "heading",
      "field": "title",
      "fr": "Manque de traçabilité",
      "en": "Lack of traceability"
    },
    {
      "widget_id": "k6qn4vkc",
      "type": "text-editor",
      "field": "editor",
      "fr": "<p>Des données dispersées entre les machines, les feuilles Excel et les courriels nuisent à la traçabilité des pièces et commandes.</p>",
      "en": "<p>Data scattered across machines, Excel spreadsheets, and emails undermines the traceability of parts and orders.</p>"
    },
    {
      "widget_id": "ygnleuwz",
      "type": "heading",
      "field": "title",
      "fr": "Problèmes de version",
      "en": "Versioning issues"
    },
    {
      "widget_id": "ayuzu804",
      "type": "text-editor",
      "field": "editor",
      "fr": "<p>Des fichiers CAO en double ou mal nommés engendrent des erreurs en production, des retouches coûteuses et des retards.</p>",
      "en": "<p>Duplicated or poorly named CAD files lead to production errors, costly rework, and delays.</p>"
    },
    {
      "widget_id": "y3whz48o",
      "type": "heading",
      "field": "title",
      "fr": "Bureau ↔ atelier désynchronisé",
      "en": "Office ↔ workshop disconnect"
    },
    {
      "widget_id": "chpw2lkv",
      "type": "text-editor",
      "field": "editor",
      "fr": "<p>Des allers-retours manuels ou l'absence de PDM freinent la mise en production rapide et sécurisée.</p>",
      "en": "<p>Manual back-and-forth or the absence of PDM slows down fast and secure production launches.</p>"
    },
    {
      "widget_id": "hu5akl1r",
      "type": "heading",
      "field": "title",
      "fr": "Documents techniques perdus",
      "en": "Lost technical documents"
    },
    {
      "widget_id": "2onrvfvk",
      "type": "text-editor",
      "field": "editor",
      "fr": "<p>Plans, fiches techniques et instructions sont stockés localement, rendant leur accès difficile et leur mise à jour aléatoire.</p>",
      "en": "<p>Drawings, datasheets, and instructions stored locally are hard to access and unreliable to update.</p>"
    },
    {
      "widget_id": "xc26tsc7",
      "type": "heading",
      "field": "title",
      "fr": "Suivi de projet difficile",
      "en": "Difficult project tracking"
    },
    {
      "widget_id": "fc2g7hv9",
      "type": "text-editor",
      "field": "editor",
      "fr": "<p>Sans outil structurant, les échéances, les statuts et les versions deviennent rapidement opaques pour toute l'équipe.</p>",
      "en": "<p>Without a structuring tool, deadlines, statuses, and versions quickly become opaque to the whole team.</p>"
    },
    {
      "widget_id": "0e2ys7v8",
      "type": "heading",
      "field": "title",
      "fr": "Sécurité des données",
      "en": "Data security"
    },
    {
      "widget_id": "2ayp68rn",
      "type": "text-editor",
      "field": "editor",
      "fr": "<p>Sauvegardes incomplètes, accès non contrôlés : vos données techniques critiques sont exposées sans cadre clair.</p>",
      "en": "<p>Incomplete backups, uncontrolled access: your critical technical data is exposed without a clear framework.</p>"
    },
    {
      "widget_id": "lii9fxti",
      "type": "heading",
      "field": "title",
      "fr": "BÉNÉFICES",
      "en": "BENEFITS"
    },
    {
      "widget_id": "eq0ibewj",
      "type": "heading",
      "field": "title",
      "fr": "Ce que vous gagnez <em style=\"font-family:Fraunces,serif;font-style:italic;color:#C9A35C;font-weight:600\">concrètement</em>",
      "en": "What you gain <em style=\"font-family:Fraunces,serif;font-style:italic;color:#C9A35C;font-weight:600\">concretely</em>"
    },
    {
      "widget_id": "a2thvxlf",
      "type": "text-editor",
      "field": "editor",
      "fr": "<p>Une approche structurée pour reprendre le contrôle sur vos données techniques et fluidifier votre production.</p>",
      "en": "<p>A structured approach to regain control over your technical data and streamline your production.</p>"
    },
